WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Creating an inspection in RestoreAssist is fast and thorough.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Start by entering the job address — our geocoding finds it automatically.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
Select the claim type — water damage, mould, fire, or smoke.

00:24.000 --> 00:29.294
Add the claim number and insurer.

00:29.294 --> 00:37.294
Capture photos and moisture readings directly in the app.

00:37.294 --> 00:45.294
Every entry is timestamped and signed off with digital signatures.

00:45.294 --> 00:49.144
Submit, and you're done.